| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3959 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 27dedfdd-57ac-50ac-bf8d-8d06536d7b4d"
